    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2014 Porsche Cayman (981) represents a pinnacle of mid-engine balance and mechanical engagement. Driven by a 2.7L naturally aspirated flat-six, the powerplant delivers linear torque and a visceral soundtrack through its high-revving range. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain provides an unfiltered connection to the road. The chassis features optimized suspension geometry with robust McPherson struts and four-piston aluminum monoblock fixed calipers for exceptional deceleration. This example remains mechanically sound with a documented service history, showcasing tight tolerances and responsive throttle mapping. It is a driver-focused machine that prioritizes tactile feedback and lateral grip, currently presented in a well-maintained state suitable for immediate spirited use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
