      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. Finished in a timeless metallic coat, the exterior retains a high-gloss shine with only minor, expected road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every electronic feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is in excellent health, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and oil service. It starts smoothly, shifts flawlessly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. With a documented service history and a smoke-free interior, this car is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
