    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a brand-new adventure! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-cared for, drives like a dream, and is totally ready to hit the road with you today. It's the perfect match for someone who wants a dependable, high-quality vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. I'd love for you to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love how it handles!",
